<seg id="717">Regulations of German and Czech public procurement law</seg>
<seg id="718">Same or similar regulations</seg>
<seg id="719">Both countries have implemented EU rules on information and verification procedures.</seg>
<seg id="720">In both countries, the award authority has to decide on the award of the contract.</seg>
<seg id="721">However, it must not arbitrarily deviate from the result of a proper examination and evaluation of the offers.</seg>
